People's yearning for a better life is our goal
(November 15, 2012)
Journalists have made a lot of reports on the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China, conveying many "Chinese voices" to the world.
On behalf of the General Assembly Secretariat, I would like to express my heartfelt thanks to all of you.
Just now, we held the first plenary meeting of the 18th Central Committee of the Communist Party of China, elected a new leadership of the Central Committee, and elected me as General Secretary of the Central Committee.
On behalf of the members of the new leadership of the Central Committee, I would like to thank all the comrades in the party for their trust, and I will definitely live up to the heavy trust and mission.
The great trust of all the comrades in the party and the expectations of the people of all ethnic groups in the country is a great encouragement for us to do a good job in our work, and it is also a great responsibility on our shoulders.
This great responsibility is the responsibility to the nation.
Our nation is a great nation.
During more than 5,000 years of civilization development, the Chinese nation has made an indelible contribution to the progress of human civilization.
After modern times, our nation has gone through hardships, and the Chinese nation has come to the most dangerous time.
Since then, in order to realize the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation, countless people with lofty ideals have fought and failed again and again.
After the founding of the Communist Party of China, the Communist Party of China has united and led the people to work tirelessly to turn the poor and backward old China into a new China that is increasingly prosperous and strong. The great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation has shown unprecedented bright prospects.
Our responsibility is to unite and lead the whole party and the people of all ethnic groups in the country, take over the baton of history, and continue to work hard for the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation, so that the Chinese nation can stand stronger and stronger among the nations of the world, and make new contributions to mankind. greater contribution.
This great responsibility is the responsibility to the people.
Our people are great people.
In the long historical process, the Chinese people, relying on their own diligence, courage and wisdom, have created a beautiful homeland where all ethnic groups live in harmony and cultivated an excellent culture that lasts forever.
Our people love life and look forward to better education, more stable jobs, more satisfactory income, more reliable social security, higher level of medical and health services, more comfortable living conditions, and a more beautiful environment. Hope the children can grow up better, work better and live better.
The people's yearning for a better life is our goal.
All happiness in the world requires hard work to create.
Our responsibility is to unite and lead the whole party and the people of all ethnic groups in the country, continue to emancipate their minds, adhere to reform and opening up, continuously liberate and develop social productive forces, strive to solve the difficulties in production and life of the masses, and unswervingly follow the path of common prosperity.
This important responsibility is the responsibility to the party.
Our party is a party that serves the people wholeheartedly.
The Party has led the people to achieve world-renowned achievements, and we have every reason to be proud of this, but we are proud and not complacent, and we will never rest on the merits of the past.
Under the new situation, our party is facing many severe challenges, and there are many problems that need to be solved urgently within the party.
In particular, the problems of corruption, alienation from the masses, formalism, bureaucracy and other issues that have occurred among some party members and cadres must be resolved with great efforts.
The whole party must wake up.
Blacksmith need its own hardware.
Our responsibility is to work with all the comrades of the party to insist that the party should manage the party and run the party strictly, effectively solve its own outstanding problems, effectively improve the work style, and keep close contact with the masses, so that our party will always become a leader in the cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics. Strong leadership core.
The people are the creators of history, and the masses are the true heroes.
The people are the source of our strength.
We deeply know that each person's strength is limited, but as long as we are united and united, there will be no difficulties that cannot be overcome; each person's working time is limited, but serving the people wholeheartedly is unlimited.
The responsibility is heavier than Mount Tai, and the career has a long way to go.
We must always have a heart-to-heart bond with the people, share weal and woe with the people, and struggle in unity with the people.
China needs to know more about the world, and the world needs to know more about China.
It is hoped that friends from the journalists will continue to make more efforts and contributions to enhancing mutual understanding between China and other countries in the world.
Closely focus on upholding and developing socialism with Chinese characteristics, study, publicize and implement the spirit of the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China
(November 17, 2012)
The report of the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China outlines a grand blueprint for building a moderately prosperous society in an all-round way, accelerating socialist modernization, and winning new victories for socialism with Chinese characteristics under new historical conditions. The political declaration and action plan of continuing to advance on the path of socialism and striving to build a moderately prosperous society in an all-round way have pointed out the direction for the work of this session of the central leadership.
The Central Committee has issued a notice on earnestly studying, propagating and implementing the spirit of the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China.
The 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China emphasized the need to hold high the great banner of socialism with Chinese characteristics, stressed that socialism with Chinese characteristics is the fundamental achievement of the Party and the people's struggle, creation and accumulation for more than 90 years, which must be cherished, persisted, and continuously developed, and called on the whole party to make unremitting exploration. And grasp the laws of socialism with Chinese characteristics, maintain the vitality of the party forever, maintain the impetus for national development, and strive to open up broader prospects for the development of socialism with Chinese characteristics.
It can be said that upholding and developing socialism with Chinese characteristics is a main thread running through the report of the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China.
We must firmly grasp this main line, and regard upholding and developing socialism with Chinese characteristics as the focus, focus, and foothold of studying and implementing the spirit of the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China. Only in this way can we learn more about the spirit of the 18th National Congress of the Party. Go deeper, understand more thoroughly, and implement more consciously.
Why am I stressing this point?
This is because the long-term practice of the party and the country has fully proved that only socialism can save China, and only socialism with Chinese characteristics can develop China.
Only by holding high the great banner of socialism with Chinese characteristics can we unite and lead the whole party and the people of all ethnic groups to build a moderately prosperous society in all respects when the Communist Party of China is 100 years old, and build a modern socialist country that is prosperous, strong, democratic, culturally advanced and harmonious when the new China is 100 years old. Win a happier and better future for the Chinese people and the Chinese nation.
Focusing on adhering to and developing socialism with Chinese characteristics, studying, publicizing and implementing the spirit of the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China, I understand that the following aspects should be grasped from the combination of theory and practice.
First, a profound understanding of socialism with Chinese characteristics is a fundamental achievement achieved by the party and the people through long-term practice.
Socialism with Chinese characteristics was created in the new era of reform and opening up, and it is also based on the long-term struggle of our party. Relay exploration obtained.
Relying closely on the people, our party has fundamentally changed the future and destiny of the Chinese people and the Chinese nation, irreversibly ending the tragic fate of China's domestic and foreign troubles, poverty and weakness since modern times, and irreversibly opening the door to the continuous development and growth of the Chinese nation. , The historical march towards the great rejuvenation makes the Chinese nation with a history of more than 5,000 years of civilization stand in the forest of the world's nations with a brand-new attitude.
We must always remember the historic contributions made by the three generations of the Party's central leadership and the Party Central Committee with Comrade Hu Jintao as General Secretary to socialism with Chinese characteristics.
The first generation of the party's central leadership with Comrade Mao Zedong at its core provided valuable experience, theoretical preparation, and material basis for the creation of socialism with Chinese characteristics in the new era.
The second generation of the party's central leadership with Comrade Deng Xiaoping at its core successfully created socialism with Chinese characteristics.
The party's third-generation central collective leadership with Comrade Jiang Zemin at its core has successfully pushed socialism with Chinese characteristics into the 21st century.
In the new stage of the new century, the CPC Central Committee with Comrade Hu Jintao as General Secretary has succeeded in upholding and developing socialism with Chinese characteristics at a new historical starting point.
It can be seen that socialism with Chinese characteristics carries the ideals and explorations of several generations of Chinese Communists, embodies the long-cherished wishes and expectations of countless people with lofty ideals, and embodies the struggle and sacrifice of hundreds of millions of people. It is an inevitable choice for the development of Chinese society in modern times. , is the only way to develop and stabilize China.
Practice has fully proved that socialism with Chinese characteristics is the banner of unity, progress and victory of the Communist Party of China and the Chinese people.
To build a moderately prosperous society in an all-round way, accelerate socialist modernization, and realize the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation, we must always hold high the great banner of socialism with Chinese characteristics and unswervingly adhere to and develop socialism with Chinese characteristics.
The 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China required the whole party to have firm confidence in the path, theory, and system of socialism with Chinese characteristics. This is the fundamental reason.
Second, profoundly understand that socialism with Chinese characteristics is composed of the three-in-one road, theoretical system and system.
The 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China clarified the scientific connotation of the road of socialism with Chinese characteristics, the theoretical system of socialism with Chinese characteristics, and the system of socialism with Chinese characteristics and their interrelationships, emphasizing that the road of socialism with Chinese characteristics is the way to achieve, and the theoretical system of socialism with Chinese characteristics It is a guide for action, the system of socialism with Chinese characteristics is the fundamental guarantee, and the three are unified in the great practice of socialism with Chinese characteristics.
This is the most distinctive feature of socialism with Chinese characteristics.
This summary tells us that socialism with Chinese characteristics is a close combination of practice, theory and system. It not only elevates successful practice to theory, but also guides new practice with correct theory, and timely upgrades the principles and policies that have achieved results in practice. system for the party and the state.
Therefore, socialism with Chinese characteristics is especially in its path, theoretical system, and system, especially in the internal connection of its realization methods, action guidelines, and fundamental guarantees, and especially in the unity of these three in socialism with Chinese characteristics. Great in practice.
In contemporary China, upholding and developing socialism with Chinese characteristics means truly upholding socialism.
The road of socialism with Chinese characteristics is the only way to realize my country's socialist modernization and the only way to create a better life for the people.
The road of socialism with Chinese characteristics not only adheres to economic construction as the center, but also comprehensively promotes economic construction, political construction, cultural construction, social construction, ecological civilization construction and other constructions; it not only adheres to the four basic principles, but also adheres to reform and opening up; Not only continuously liberate and develop social productive forces, but also gradually realize the common prosperity of all people and promote the all-round development of people.
The theoretical system of socialism with Chinese characteristics is the latest achievement of the Sinicization of Marxism, including Deng Xiaoping Theory, the important thought of "Three Represents" and the Scientific Outlook on Development.
Marxism-Leninism and Mao Zedong Thought must not be lost.
At the same time, we must focus on the practical problems of our country's reform, opening up and modernization drive and what we are doing, focus on the application of Marxist theory, focus on theoretical thinking on practical problems, focus on new practices and new develop.
In contemporary China, adhering to the theoretical system of socialism with Chinese characteristics is truly adhering to Marxism.
The socialist system with Chinese characteristics insists on organically combining the fundamental political system, the basic political system with the basic economic system, as well as specific systems such as various systems and mechanisms; The organic combination of people being the masters of the country and ruling the country according to law conforms to my country's national conditions, embodies the characteristics and advantages of socialism with Chinese characteristics, and is the fundamental institutional guarantee for China's development and progress.
It should be noted that the socialist system with Chinese characteristics is distinctive and efficient, but it is not perfect and mature.
The cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics continues to develop, and the socialist system with Chinese characteristics also needs to be continuously improved.
Comrade Deng Xiaoping pointed out in his visit to the South in 1992: "I am afraid it will take another 30 years before we have formed a more mature and stereotyped system in all aspects."
The 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China emphasized that system construction should be placed in a prominent position and the advantages of my country's socialist political system should be brought into full play.
We must insist on promoting institutional innovation through theoretical innovation based on practice, adhere to and improve the existing system, proceed from reality, formulate some new systems in a timely manner, and build a system that is complete, scientifically standardized, and effective in operation, so as to make all aspects of the system more efficient. Mature and more stereotyped, providing a more effective institutional guarantee for the new victory of socialism with Chinese characteristics.
Third, deeply understand the general basis, general layout, and general tasks of building socialism with Chinese characteristics.
The Eighteenth National Congress of the Communist Party of China emphasized that the general basis for building socialism with Chinese characteristics is the primary stage of socialism, the general layout is five in one, and the general task is to realize socialist modernization and the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation.
The summary of the "three generals" is high-level, concise, and concise.
A deep understanding and grasp of this new generalization will help us to deeply understand and grasp the true meaning and essence of socialism with Chinese characteristics.
The general basis is emphasized because the primary stage of socialism is the greatest national condition and greatest reality of contemporary China.
Under any circumstances, we must firmly grasp the greatest national conditions, and to promote reform and development in any area must firmly base itself on this greatest reality.
Not only should we always base ourselves on the primary stage in economic construction, but also in political construction, cultural construction, social construction, and ecological civilization construction should always keep the primary stage in mind; After improving, keep the primary stage in mind; not only when planning long-term development, but also keep the primary stage in mind in daily work.
The party's basic line in the primary stage of socialism is the lifeline of the party and the country.
In practice, we must always adhere to "one center, two basic points" unswervingly, neither deviate from "one center" nor neglect "two basic points", and put the practice of the common ideal of socialism with Chinese characteristics and firm communism together. Unity with lofty ideals, resolutely resist all kinds of wrong ideas about abandoning socialism, and consciously correct wrong ideas and policy measures that go beyond the stage.
Only in this way can we truly achieve neither underestimation nor arrogance, and earnestly win new victories of socialism with Chinese characteristics.
Emphasis on the general layout is because socialism with Chinese characteristics is socialism with all-round development.
We must firmly grasp the top priority of the party's governance and rejuvenation of the country, always represent the development requirements of China's advanced productive forces, adhere to economic construction as the center, and on the basis of continuous economic development, coordinate the promotion of political construction, cultural construction, social construction, ecological construction Civilization construction and other aspects of construction.
With the deepening of my country's economic and social development, the status and role of ecological civilization construction has become increasingly prominent.
The 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China incorporated the construction of ecological civilization into the overall layout of socialism with Chinese characteristics, which made the strategic position of ecological civilization construction more clear, and was conducive to integrating ecological civilization construction into economic construction, political construction, cultural construction, and social construction. process.
This is an important result of our Party's continuous deepening of practice and understanding of the laws of socialist construction.
In accordance with this general layout, we must promote the coordination of all aspects of the modernization drive, and promote the coordination between production relations and productive forces, superstructure and economic foundation.
The general task is emphasized because our party has shouldered the historical mission of realizing the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation since the day it was founded.
Our Party leads the people to carry out revolutionary construction and reforms to make the Chinese people prosperous, the country prosperous, and to revitalize the great Chinese nation.
In accordance with the strategic deployment of the "three-step" modernization drive, building a modern socialist country that is prosperous, strong, democratic, culturally advanced, and harmonious is the goal of our party and country in the entire primary stage of socialism.
The solemn mission of our party, the fundamental purpose of reform and opening up, and the goal of our country's struggle all focus on and boil down to this general task.
We must firmly hold on to this general task and persevere from generation to generation.
In different historical periods, our party has always put forward inspiring goals in accordance with the will of the people and the needs of career development, and united and led the people to strive for it.
The 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of my country has enriched and improved the goal of building a moderately prosperous society in an all-round way in accordance with the new changes in the domestic and international situation, and in line with the new economic and social development of our country and the new expectations of the general public. To better meet the new requirements of the people's will.
These goals and requirements are in line with the goal of building a moderately prosperous society in an all-round way put forward by the 16th National Congress of the Communist Party of China and the new requirements of realizing the goal of building a moderately prosperous society in an all-round way put forward by the Seventeenth National Congress of the Communist Party of China, and are also consistent with the overall layout of the cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics.
The whole party and the whole country should work with one heart and one mind, work hard, be determined to innovate, forge ahead, and work together to achieve the goals of building a moderately prosperous society in an all-round way and deepening reform and opening-up proposed at the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China.
Fourth, profoundly understand the basic requirements for winning a new victory for socialism with Chinese characteristics.
The 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China put forward the basic requirements that must be firmly grasped to win the new victory of socialism with Chinese characteristics under the new historical conditions.
These basic requirements are based on the Party's basic theory, basic line, basic program, and basic experience, and are put forward by profoundly summarizing the practice of my country's socialist construction, especially the construction of socialism with Chinese characteristics, over the past 60 years. They are the most essential things and reflect the ruling law of the Communist Party , the laws of socialist construction, and the laws of the development of human society, indicating that our party's understanding of the laws of socialism with Chinese characteristics has reached a new level.
The basic requirements put forward by the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China further answered the basic question of how to win the new victory of socialism with Chinese characteristics on the new historical journey.
Socialism with Chinese characteristics is the cause of hundreds of millions of people themselves, so we must give full play to the people's sense of ownership to better ensure that the people are the masters of the country.
Liberation and development of social productive forces is the fundamental task of socialism with Chinese characteristics, so we must adhere to economic development as the center and scientific development as the theme to achieve people-oriented, comprehensive, coordinated and sustainable scientific development.
Reform and opening up is the only way to uphold and develop socialism with Chinese characteristics. Therefore, we must always implement the spirit of reform and innovation in all aspects of state governance, and continuously promote the self-improvement and development of my country's socialist system.
Fairness and justice are the inherent requirements of socialism with Chinese characteristics. Therefore, on the basis of the common struggle of all people and economic and social development, we must step up the construction of a system that plays a major role in ensuring social fairness and justice, and gradually establish a social fairness guarantee system.
Common prosperity is the fundamental principle of socialism with Chinese characteristics. Therefore, we must make the fruits of development more and more equitable to benefit all people, and make steady progress towards common prosperity.
Social harmony is the essential attribute of socialism with Chinese characteristics, so we must unite all forces that can be united, maximize the factors of harmony, enhance social creativity, and ensure that people live and work in peace and contentment, society is stable and orderly, and the country is long-lasting.
Peaceful development is the inevitable choice of socialism with Chinese characteristics. Therefore, we must adhere to open development, cooperative development, and win-win development, expand the convergence of interests with all parties, and promote the building of a harmonious world of lasting peace and common prosperity.
The Communist Party of China is the core of leadership in the cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics, so it is necessary to strengthen and improve the leadership of the party, and give full play to the party's core leadership role in taking over the overall situation and coordinating all parties.
The basic requirements put forward by the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China are a positive response to the outstanding problems existing in my country's economic and social development, the difficult problems faced by reform and speeding up the transformation of the economic development mode, and the hot issues that cadres and the masses are generally concerned about. Entering the decisive stage of building a moderately prosperous society in an all-round way is the correct guidance for reform, development and stability, internal affairs, foreign affairs and national defense, and governance of the party, the country and the army.
These basic requirements involve not only productive forces and production relations, but also the economic base and superstructure, not only the great cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics, but also the great new project of party building, and at the same time coordinating both domestic and international situations.
The 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China has followed and embodied these basic requirements in the planning and deployment of various tasks.
By grasping these basic requirements, we will be able to better gather our strength, overcome difficulties, continue to promote scientific development, promote social harmony, continue to improve people's lives, enhance people's well-being, and complete the glorious and arduous tasks entrusted by the times.
Fifth, deeply understand and ensure that the party will always be the strong leadership core of the cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics.
The 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China emphasized that our party shoulders the important task of uniting and leading the people to build a moderately prosperous society in an all-round way, promote socialist modernization, and realize the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation.
If the Party is strong and strong, and the Party maintains flesh-and-blood ties with the people, the country will be prosperous and stable, and the people will be happy and healthy.
The development of the situation, the development of the cause, and the expectations of the people all require us to comprehensively promote the new great project of party building with the spirit of reform and innovation, and comprehensively improve the scientific level of party building.
Governing the country must first govern the party, and governing the party must be strict.
To this end, the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China put forward the general requirements and various tasks to comprehensively improve the scientific level of party building under the new situation.
The whole party must deeply study and comprehend it and implement it one by one.
The general requirements for party building put forward by the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China are not only aimed at inheriting and carrying forward the fundamental point of maintaining and developing the advanced nature of our party's Marxist party for more than 90 years, but also focusing on adapting to and responding to the world conditions under the new situation. , new changes in national conditions and party conditions.
Over the years, we have comprehensively advanced the new great project of party building, the party's governance capacity has been newly improved, the party's advanced nature and purity have been maintained and developed, and the party's leadership has been strengthened and improved.
At the same time, compared with the development and changes of domestic and foreign situations, and compared with the historical tasks undertaken by the Party, there is still a considerable gap in the Party's leadership and governance level, the construction of Party organizations, and the quality, ability, and style of Party members and cadres.
Especially in the new situation, strengthening and improving the party building is faced with "four tests" and "four dangers", and the task of implementing the party's management of the party and the strict management of the party is more arduous and urgent than ever before.
The whole party must enhance the sense of urgency and responsibility, firmly grasp the general requirements of party building, continuously improve the party's leadership and governance level, and improve the ability to resist corruption, change and risk, so that our party can be in the historical process of profound changes in the world situation. It has always been at the forefront of the times, has always been the backbone of the people of the whole country in the historical process of coping with various risks and tests at home and abroad, and has always been a strong leadership core in the historical process of upholding and developing socialism with Chinese characteristics.
Strengthening ideals and beliefs and sticking to the spiritual pursuit of the Communists have always been the foundation for the Communists to settle down.
Belief in Marxism, socialism and communism is the political soul of communists and the spiritual pillar for communists to withstand any test.
Figuratively speaking, ideals and beliefs are the spiritual "calcium" of communists. Without ideals and beliefs, if ideals and beliefs are not firm, they will be mentally "deficient in calcium" and suffer from "rickets."
In real life, some party members and cadres have problems of one kind or another. In the final analysis, they are lost in their beliefs and spirits.
The entire party must, in accordance with the deployment of the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China, thoroughly study and practice the theoretical system of socialism with Chinese characteristics, especially the scientific concept of development, emphasize party spirit, pay attention to conduct, set an example, and be determined to strive for the realization of the common ideal of socialism with Chinese characteristics.
Close relations between the party and the masses, cadres and masses, and maintaining flesh-and-blood ties with the people have always been the foundation of our party's invincible position.
The future and destiny of a political party and a regime ultimately depend on the backing of the people.
If we are disconnected from the masses and lose the support and support of the people, we will also eventually fail.
We must adapt to the new characteristics and new requirements of mass work under the new situation, do a good job in organizing, publicizing, educating and serving the masses, learn from the masses with an open mind, accept the supervision of the masses sincerely, always take root in the people, benefit the people, and always maintain the Party The flesh-and-blood connection with the people has always been heart-to-heart, breath and common destiny with the people.
It is necessary to draw wisdom and strength from the great practice of the people, do a good job of obeying the will of the people, relieve the people's worries, and benefit the people's livelihood, and correct the behavior that damages the interests of the people.
The 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China proposed that the party's mass line education and practice activities should be carried out in the whole party with pragmatism and honesty as the main content.
The central government will make arrangements for this activity, and party committees at all levels must earnestly implement it, focus on solving outstanding problems that the people have strongly reflected on, and ensure that the activity is effective.
Opposing corruption, building clean politics, and maintaining the party's physical health have always been our party's clear political stance.
The construction of party conduct and clean government is a major political issue that the majority of cadres and masses have always paid attention to.
