In the Preface to the Critique of Political Economy, Marx said: "In the social production of their own lives, people have a definite, inevitable, and independent relationship with their will, that is, with a certain stage of development of their material productive forces. suitable production relations.
The sum total of these relations of production constitutes the economic structure of society, the actual foundation upon which a legal and political superstructure is erected and to which a certain form of social consciousness corresponds. "
In the comprehensive deepening of reform, we must adhere to the economic system reform as the main axis, and strive to achieve new breakthroughs in the reform of important areas and key links, so as to lead and drive reforms in other areas, so that the reforms in all aspects can be promoted in concert and form a synergy, rather than Separate governance and decentralize efforts.
Fourth, adhere to the direction of socialist market economic reform.
Proposing the reform goal of establishing a socialist market economic system is a major theoretical and practical innovation of our party in the process of building socialism with Chinese characteristics, and it has solved a major problem that other socialist countries in the world have not solved for a long time.
For more than 20 years, we have promoted the reform of the economic system and other aspects of the system around the goal of establishing a socialist market economic system, so that our country has successfully realized the transformation from a highly centralized planned economic system to a vigorous socialist market economic system, from a closed and semi-closed economic system. The great historical transition from being closed to all-round opening has achieved a historic leap in people's lives from subsistence and clothing to a moderately prosperous society, achieved a historic leap in the world's second largest economy, and greatly mobilized the enthusiasm of hundreds of millions of people. It has promoted the development of social productive forces and greatly enhanced the vitality of the party and the country.
At the same time, we must also see that although my country's socialist market economic system has been initially established, the market system is not perfect, the market development is not sufficient, especially the relationship between the government and the market has not been straightened out, and the role of the market in resource allocation Effective performance is subject to many constraints, and hard work is still needed to achieve the strategic task of accelerating the improvement of the socialist market economic system proposed at the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China.
Adhering to the direction of socialist market economic reform, the core issue is to properly handle the relationship between the government and the market, so that the market can play a decisive role in resource allocation and the government can better play its role.
This is another major advance of our party in theory and practice.
Adhering to the direction of the socialist market economic reform is not only the basic adherence to the reform of the economic system, but also an important basis for comprehensively deepening the reform.
Making the market play a decisive role in resource allocation mainly involves the reform of the economic system, but will inevitably affect various fields such as politics, culture, society, ecological civilization and party building.
It is necessary to make the institutional reforms in all aspects move forward in a coordinated manner towards the establishment of a sound socialist market economic system, and at the same time make the relevant links of all aspects better adapt to the new requirements put forward by the development of the socialist market economy.
Fifth, take the promotion of social fairness and justice and the well-being of the people as the starting point and goal.
Since the reform and opening up, my country has made great achievements in economic and social development, providing a solid material foundation and favorable conditions for promoting social fairness and justice.
